data.description: Nestled on a spacious .43-acre lot in the city of Grand Haven, this charming ranch boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Conveniently positioned near schools and a variety of dining options, this home features a generously sized primary suite with an en suite bathroom for added privacy. The warm and inviting family room is the perfect setting for relaxation, while the lower level offers a versatile bedroom, laundry facilities, and additional flex space ideal for a home office setup. The property is complemented by an attached one-stall garage with an expanded workshop area for your creative projects. Step outside to enjoy the large, fenced backyard- a secure space for pets to roam and a perfect space for all of your outdoor activities.
